Add more luxury to your home with 100% pure cashmere items. #NAKEDHOMEwithAshleyStark

How to enter:
✔️Follow @nakedcashmere and @ashleytstark 
✔️Like this photo and @nakedcashmere's sweepstakes photo posted on 8/5
✔️Tag 3 people in your life who love home décor 
*For an extra entry: Share this post on Instagram Stories and tag us both! 

Giveaway ends Monday 8/9 at 11:59PM PST, winners will be announced on @nakedcashmere’s sweepstakes post. Open to ages 21+, available to global audiences, no purchase necessary. For the official rules, visit nakedcashmere.com/nakedrules GOOD LUCK! #NakedInCashmere

I’m proud to launch a 100% pure cashmere Home Collection with @NakedCashmere today! NAKEDCASHMERE has been a favorite of mine for years, when designing this collection I wanted to invoke that same feeling of coziness, yet chicness; with lots of layers and textures. This sustainable 18-piece collection brings the ultimate level of luxury into your everyday life.
